<head>
    <title>Post-Mortem - Manage your incidente to 360</title>
    <%- include ('./_head.ejs') %>
</head>
<body>

<%- include ('./_header.ejs') %>


<a name="how-it-works"></a>
<div class="bg-white">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="relative mt-6 pb-32 bg-gray-800">
        <div class="absolute inset-0">
            <img class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                 src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1525130413817-d45c1d127c42?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1920&q=60&&sat=-100"
                 alt="">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gray-800 mix-blend-multiply" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto py-24 px-4 sm:py-32 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <span class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-white md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">Write and execute post-mortem like the <br><span
                        class='block text-green-500 xl:inline'>big one</span>
            </span>
            <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-xl text-gray-300">Post-mortem.app is your online war room for incident communication centralization, take actions and follow them.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Overlapping cards -->
    <section class="-mt-32 max-w-7xl mx-auto relative z-10 pb-32 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"
             aria-labelledby="contact-heading">
        <h2 class="sr-only" id="contact-heading">Free your data</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-y-20 lg:grid-cols-3 lg:gap-y-0 lg:gap-x-8">
            <div class="flex flex-col bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl">
                <div class="card flex-1 relative pt-16 px-6 pb-6 md:px-8">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 p-5 inline-block bg-green-400 rounded-xl shadow-lg transform -translate-y-1/2">
                        <!-- Heroicon -->
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                             stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                                  d="M3 10h18M7 15h1m4 0h1m-7 4h12a3 3 0 003-3V8a3 3 0 00-3-3H6a3 3 0 00-3 3v8a3 3 0 003 3z" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-900">1 - Create and invite your team</h3>
                    <p class="mt-4 text-base text-gray-500">Create a <strong>free account</strong> to access to post-mortem with your personal or professional email.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl">
                <div class="card flex-1 relative pt-16 px-6 pb-6 md:px-8">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 p-5 inline-block bg-green-400 rounded-xl shadow-lg transform -translate-y-1/2">
                        <!-- Heroicon -->
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                             stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                                  d="M13.828 10.172a4 4 0 00-5.656 0l-4 4a4 4 0 105.656 5.656l1.102-1.101m-.758-4.899a4 4 0 005.656 0l4-4a4 4 0 00-5.656-5.656l-1.1 1.1" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-900">2 - Declare your first incident</h3>
                    <p class="mt-4 text-base text-gray-500">When an incident starts, open post-mortem.app and starts filling the timeline. Write down mitigations, actions and automate your internal/external communications through the app. Expose your public incidents page. </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl">
                <div class="card flex-1 relative pt-16 px-6 pb-6 md:px-8">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 p-5 inline-block bg-green-400 rounded-xl shadow-lg transform -translate-y-1/2">
                        <!-- Heroicon -->
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                             stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                                  d="M4 8V4m0 0h4M4 4l5 5m11-1V4m0 0h-4m4 0l-5 5M4 16v4m0 0h4m-4 0l5-5m11 5l-5-5m5 5v-4m0 4h-4" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-900">3 - Actions follow up</h3>
                    <p class="mt-4 text-base text-gray-500">No more defined actions without real impacts. Post-mortem.app enforce actions follow up so you won't have twice the same kind of incident.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>

